🌅 Welcome to Solara Linux 🌅
═══════════════════════════════════════

Solara is a rolling Arch-based distro.
Elegant by default, not by accident.
systemd. glibc. no atomic nonsense.

Born from the ashes of:
  ✝  moonlightOS v4-v7 (rip)
  ✝  S3RLinux (archived, let it die)
  ✝  S3RLinux-Atomic (killed by NVIDIA)

We don't talk about S3RLinux-Atomic.

To install: sudo solara-install
Wi-Fi: nmtui | Desktop: SDDM

